This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with image stylization and transfer. Additionally, the use of neural networks and deep learning techniques suggests that it could also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper also involves attention mechanisms and semantic matching, which could place it in the Graphics (cs.GR) category. Finally, the use of multi-style transfer could also suggest that it belongs to the Multimedia (cs.MM) category.
